<br>
Some classes get more opportunities to play the hero.  Clerics are expected to save your butt.  Raids rely on having a monk who knows area and how to pull mobs.  Screw it up and people will notice.<br>
<br>
Few people praise the druid for helping keep main tank alive when other healers are OOM or the wizzie for timing nuke perfectly or the paladin for stunning mob that was about to gate or shaman for deliberately getting aggro and dragging mob off chanter and parking it so it can be mezzed.  They may be easier than other classes to play on day to day basis but I sure am glad that some players took the time to figure out what they can do and how to do it well.  To think that a mage is only a vending machine or that all a necro does is twitch is selling them short.  They and other support classes can fill other roles if given the opportunity.<br>
<br>
I guess what I am trying to say is that until you have played that class for a little while, it's difficult to fully appreciate it. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub54.ezboard.com/ujurorb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>JurorB</A> at: 9/16/02 5:30:43 pm<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=937.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=937.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=937.topic&start=61&stop=64>4</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=937.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=937.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=937.topic&index=40><img src=http://quellious-collective.com/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=937.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm1.threadControl?topicID=937.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=937.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquatersther